text: Novosafarovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Uryadinsky Selsoviet, Mishkinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 21 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 24 km from Mishkino, 8 km from Uryady. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mishkinsky District
title: Novosafarovo
